{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-243-resilience","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Lekcija 243: Strpljenje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pozitivna oblast čiji je indikator manji od njegove širine naziva se pravilni deo.</p>\n<p>Za bilo koji integer, $d$, postoji tačan deo $d−1$; na primer, za $d = 12$:</p>\n<p>$$\\frac{1}{12}, \\frac{2}{12}, \\frac{3}{12}, \\frac{4}{12}, \\frac{5}{12}, \\frac{6}{12}, \\frac{7}{12}, \\frac{8}{12}, \\frac{9}{12}, \\frac{10}{12}, \\frac{11}{12}$$</p>\n<p>Zove se deo koji ne može biti smanjen na manje delove, deo izdržljivosti.</p>\n<p>Nadalje, objasnićemo otpornost matrice, $R(d)$, kao omjer njenih tačnih dijelova koji su otporni; na primjer, $R(12) = \\frac{4}{11}$.</p>\n<p>Zapravo, $d = 12$ je najmanji interval sa tolerancijom $R(d) &#x3C; \\frac{4}{10}$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi najmanji interval, sa tolerancijom $R(d)$ &#x3C; \\frac{15\\,499}{94\\,744}$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4601000cf542c50ff73","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301890,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-243-resilience"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function resilience() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nresilience();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>resilience()</code> treba da vrati <code>892371480</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(resilience(), 892371480);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-pr